<p>2. English Skills</p>
<p>
    I belive the readers here should be capable enough in English skills. It is quite important to have good English skills, because the popular programming languages are generally made for English users, and the user manual may be made English-only. Good English skills help good understanding of the programming languages. I think I improve my English skills during the repeatitively research of programming answer, and read English materials in a faster pace.</p>

